   <p xml:id="50" begin="00:01:18.097" end="00:01:21.834">IT WORKS IN FAVOR OF BLACKS.</p>
   <p xml:id="51" begin="00:01:20.833" end="00:01:22.969">WHITE FELONS ARE MORE LIKELY</p>
   <p xml:id="52" begin="00:01:21.968" end="00:01:24.203">TO BE SHOT BY THE POLICE</p>
   <p xml:id="53" begin="00:01:23.102" end="00:01:25.805">FOLLOWING THE ARREST FOR</p>
   <p xml:id="54" begin="00:01:24.337" end="00:01:26.072">VIOLENT FELONIES THAN BLACKS</p>
   <p xml:id="55" begin="00:01:25.938" end="00:01:27.407">ARE.</p>
   <p xml:id="56" begin="00:01:26.205" end="00:01:30.376">&gt;&gt; ISN'T THAT STUNNING?</p>
   <p xml:id="57" begin="00:01:27.540" end="00:01:32.078">&gt;&gt; IT'S ONE OF THREE OTHER</p>
   <p xml:id="58" begin="00:01:30.510" end="00:01:33.012">STUDIES THIS YEAR ALONE,</p>
   <p xml:id="59" begin="00:01:32.211" end="00:01:34.814">BILL.</p>
   <p xml:id="60" begin="00:01:33.146" end="00:01:35.481">THAT HAVE SHOWN THAT</p>
   <p xml:id="61" begin="00:01:34.947" end="00:01:37.483">EVERYTHING THAT BLACK LIVES</p>
   <p xml:id="62" begin="00:01:35.615" end="00:01:45.591">MATTER NARRATIVE HAS BEEN</p>
   <p xml:id="63" begin="00:01:37.617" end="00:01:46.426">PUSHING OUT IS WRONG REVERSE</p>
   <p xml:id="64" begin="00:01:45.725" end="00:01:46.993">IT AND YOU HAVE GOT THE</p>
   <p xml:id="65" begin="00:01:46.559" end="00:01:49.996">TRUTH.</p>
   <p xml:id="66" begin="00:01:47.126" end="00:01:51.364">&gt;&gt; THIS GROUP CENTER FOR</p>
   <p xml:id="67" begin="00:01:50.129" end="00:01:53.166">EQUITY SAYS LETHAL FORCE ON</p>
   <p xml:id="68" begin="00:01:51.497" end="00:01:55.101">BLACK STUDENTS -- STUDENTS,</p>
   <p xml:id="69" begin="00:01:53.299" end="00:01:56.903">CITIZENS.</p>
   <p xml:id="70" begin="00:01:55.234" end="00:01:59.305">IS 6.92% IN ALL.</p>
   <p xml:id="71" begin="00:01:57.036" end="00:01:59.606">LETHAL FORCE ON WHITES</p>
   <p xml:id="72" begin="00:01:59.439" end="00:02:00.707">16.70.</p>
   <p xml:id="73" begin="00:01:59.739" end="00:02:01.708">SO THERE IS A BIG GAP.</p>
   <p xml:id="74" begin="00:02:00.840" end="00:02:03.009">IT'S NOT EVEN CLOSE.</p>
   <p xml:id="75" begin="00:02:01.841" end="00:02:04.511">&gt;&gt; WELL, OFFICERS ARE NOW</p>
   <p xml:id="76" begin="00:02:03.143" end="00:02:06.012">SECOND GUESSING THEMSELVES</p>
   <p xml:id="77" begin="00:02:04.644" end="00:02:06.513">WHEN THEY ARE CONFRONTING A</p>
   <p xml:id="78" begin="00:02:06.146" end="00:02:07.914">BLACK SUSPECT.</p>
   <p xml:id="79" begin="00:02:06.646" end="00:02:10.417">IN CHICAGO, THIS MONTH,</p>
   <p xml:id="80" begin="00:02:08.048" end="00:02:11.418">THERE WAS A FEMALE COP WHO</p>
   <p xml:id="81" begin="00:02:10.550" end="00:02:13.119">WAS INVOLVED IN A RESPONSE</p>
   <p xml:id="82" begin="00:02:11.551" end="00:02:15.989">TO A CAR CRASH.</p>
   <p xml:id="83" begin="00:02:13.253" end="00:02:19.692">THE SUSPECT STARTED RUNNING.</p>
   <p xml:id="84" begin="00:02:16.122" end="00:02:25.698">AND HE THEN STARTED KNOCKING</p>
   <p xml:id="85" begin="00:02:19.826" end="00:02:27.000">HER HEAD SHE LATER TOLD HER</p>
