   <p xml:id="90" begin="00:02:34.541" end="00:02:37.077">OFFICER WAS ASSAULTED AND</p>
   <p xml:id="91" begin="00:02:35.709" end="00:02:38.311">HURT BUT DIDN'T USE HER GUN</p>
   <p xml:id="92" begin="00:02:37.210" end="00:02:40.013">BECAUSE SHE WAS FEARFUL THAT</p>
