   <p xml:id="94" begin="00:02:40.147" end="00:02:40.814">OUTCRY PERSON?</p>
   <p xml:id="95" begin="00:02:40.581" end="00:02:42.616">&gt;&gt; RIGHT.</p>
   <p xml:id="96" begin="00:02:40.948" end="00:02:43.017">SHE WOULD BE THE CONSTANT</p>
   <p xml:id="97" begin="00:02:42.750" end="00:02:44.518">LOOP ON TV.</p>
   <p xml:id="98" begin="00:02:43.150" end="00:02:45.519">&gt;&gt; I WANTED YOU TO RESTATE.</p>
