   <p xml:id="100" begin="00:02:45.653" end="00:02:48.789">IT'S BEEN BACKED UP BY THIS</p>
   <p xml:id="101" begin="00:02:47.421" end="00:02:50.257">STUDY FOR POLICING EQUITY</p>
   <p xml:id="102" begin="00:02:48.923" end="00:02:51.659">AND IT'S BEEN BACKED UP BY</p>
   <p xml:id="103" begin="00:02:50.391" end="00:02:52.993">THE GALLUP POLL THAT</p>
   <p xml:id="104" begin="00:02:51.792" end="00:02:54.428">AMERICANS ARE NOT BELIEVING</p>
   <p xml:id="105" begin="00:02:53.127" end="00:02:55.262">THIS BLACK LIVES MATTER</p>
   <p xml:id="106" begin="00:02:54.562" end="00:02:56.797">PROPAGANDA THAT YOUNG BLACK</p>
