   <p xml:id="124" begin="00:03:20.955" end="00:03:22.923">AND CIVIL SOCIETY.</p>
   <p xml:id="125" begin="00:03:21.488" end="00:03:23.524">&gt;&gt; HOW MANY OTHER NEWS</p>
   <p xml:id="126" begin="00:03:23.057" end="00:03:24.925">OUTLETS DO YOU THINK IS</p>
   <p xml:id="127" begin="00:03:23.657" end="00:03:28.129">GOING TO REPORT THIS STUDY</p>
   <p xml:id="128" begin="00:03:25.059" end="00:03:28.429">AND YOUR COLUMN AND YOUR</p>
